\newlabel{fig:fnn_init}{{7}{15}{Convergence by initialisation scheme. Standard $\mathcal {N}(0,1)$ (red) triggers a gradient explosion at epoch~$\approx 75$ (MSE peaks at~3.3) but ultimately converges to the lowest test MAE. He normal/uniform converge stably and reach comparable performance}{figure.caption.20}{}}
