\newlabel{fig:fnn_evolution}{{15}{22}{Weight distribution snapshots at epochs 0, 10, 30, 100, 200 (ReLU + He normal, best config). All three layers exhibit progressive spreading from a tight initialisation to broad, learned distributions}{figure.caption.34}{}}
